    {
      "description": "<p>After drinking this potion, you can use a bonus action to exhale fire at a target within 30 feet of you. The target must make a DC 13 Dexterity saving throw, taking 4d6 fire damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. The effect tends after you exhale the fire three times or when 1 hour has passed.</p> <p class=\"indent\">This potion's orange liquid flickers, and smoke fills the top of the container and wafts out whenever it is opened.</p>",
      "id": "ID_WOTC_DMG_MAGIC_ITEM_POTION_OF_FIRE_BREATH",
      "name": "Potion of Fire Breath",
